data.description: Seller Will Pay up to 14k Towards Buyers Choice of Closing Costs OR Rate Buy Down! Check out the 3D Virtual Walkthru & Drone Video! MASSIVE 1 Owner, Brick 5bed 2.5bath approx 3200sqft + 3car Garage, Situated on almost 1/2acre w/ Charming Front Porch, Backs Up to Private Wooded Green Space! AMAZING Patio + Deck w/ Gas Hookup for Grill ~ Fire Pit ~ Exposed Natural Rock Wall ~ Landscapers Dream, Shed to Convey! Great Rm has Wood Burning OR Gas Fireplace! Hardwoods ~ Double Oven ~ Gas Cooktop ~ His & Hers Walk-In Closets ~ Water Filtration System ~ Irrigation ~ Neighborhood Pool! Not only does this Feature an Eat-In Kitchen + Formal Dining + Living + Office/Den + Open Concept Family Gathering Rm + HUGE Bonus Up, the 5thBed w/ Custom Barn Door ALSO has Endless Possibilities (2nd Office, HobbyRm, Gym, PlayRoom, etc) OR Convert to a Separate In-Law/TeenSuite) ~ Potential Expansion Space in Attic (3rd floor) & Storage Galore!
